I solved my case. Being on OS X, I use Docker via the docker-machine VM.
Both Docker and docker-machine VM have a default memory limit of 1GB, increasing both memory limits I was able to get the results without OOM errors.
@ywatanabex ,  if it may help you, using Docker stats I saw memory peak around 1.9GB

